## 0. ALLOWED AND NOT OPERATIONS
- You are only allowed to use READ operations on all of our databases. You are NOT allowed to create, change, adjust anything in our databases.
- You are only allowed to use read operations in GCP. You are NOT allowed to update, change, delete, create anything in GCP.
- You are only allowed to run read operations with git. You are NOT allowed to delete, adjust, update anything git related.


