## 4. Feature Request
If i ask you to implement a feature or fix a bug:
First provide me a plan, how you would approach it.
If there are some things unclear ask me first. When asking use numbers for your questions so i can refer to them.
Only if i ask you to skip the plan you can start executing right away.
When i ask you to test the logic if possible always try to test it just by using terminal commands.
E.g when testing an api endpoint, sending a curl command.

